      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">The health authorities couldn’t find any mistakes during their check. However, they still asked the Captain for a few cartons of cigarettes, that would help them to avoid checking the documents for a second time and trying to find some mistakes. The Captain provided a few cartons of cigarettes to the authorities in order to avoid delays.

How would the cigarettes be considered?</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" y="200" delay="0" crct="54" align="left">A bribe</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" y="260" delay="0" crct="36" align="left">A facilitation payment</txt>
